query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('android-actionbar',
'android-asynctask',
'configuration',
'keras',
'memory',
'ruby-on-rails-5',
'search',
'synchronization',
'textview',
'thread-safety',
'url-rewriting');
